text: A Libyan is a person or thing of, from, or related to Libya in North Africa. Libyan may also refer to: * A person from Libya, or of Libyan descent. For information about the Libyan people, see Demographics of Libya and Culture of Libya. For specific persons, see List of Libyans. * Libyan Arabic, a collective term for the closely related dialects of Arabic spoken in Libya. See also Languages of Libya. * Libyan cuisine == See also == *
title: Libyan (disambiguation)
